---
/**
 * About Section Component
 * Abstracts the "What NESHISE is building" module.
 */
---

<section id="studio" class="bg-pearl py-24">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-5 md:px-8">
    <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[0.8fr_1.2fr] lg:items-end">
      <div>
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-gold">What NESHISE is building</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tight md:text-5xl">An AI learning and growth ecosystem.</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">
        Inspired by high-output SEO educators and AI creator studios, NESHISE is designed as a modern platform for tutorials, blog content, resource libraries, and services that help people use AI in public, practical ways.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
